headline: WATCH LIVE: Trump and JD Vance speak at campaign rally for Dr. Oz in Pennsylvania
author: Daniel Chaitin
sentences:
Just In...
Former President Donald Trump is expected to speak at a rally in support of Senate candidate Dr. Mehmet Oz (R-PA) in Greensburg, Pennsylvania, on Friday.
Vance, the Trump-endorsed GOP Senate candidate in Ohio who won his primary Tuesday, is also expected to make an appearance.

The event was expected to start around 5 p.m., and Trump is slated to deliver remarks at 8 p.m.
J.D.
The Pennsylvania primaries are set to take place Tuesday.
